          "TITLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "Gamma-ray transitions in Tb-159 following the (n,n')",
                "reaction."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "FACILITY": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
                "facility": [
                  "VDG"
                ],
                "institute": null
              },
              "free_text": [
                " 1 MV Van de Graaff accelerator, 700 keV deuteron."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "INC-SOURCE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
                "incident_source": [
                  "D-D"
                ],
                "reaction": null
              },
              "free_text": [
                " H-2(d,n)He-3 reaction.  A freon-cooled deuteron-",
                "occluded titanium target yields about 10**8/n/sec."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "INC-SPECT": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "A cone of paraffin wax and a cylinder of lead were",
                "placed between the neutron source and the detector in",
                "order to shield the latter from direct neutron flux and",
                "direct gamma radiation.  The energy of the neutron, in",
                "this arrangement, was approximately 3.7 MeV."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "SAMPLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "99% pure terbium oxide powder packed into a thin",
                "ring-shaped polyethylene box, inner diam. of 10.8 cm",
                "and thickness 2 cm."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "DETECTOR": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "GELI"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " 40 cm3 Ge(Li) detector, with a resolution of",
                "3 keV at E(gamma)=1 MeV.  The detector was coupled to",
                "a 4096 channel analyser.",
                "The relative efficiency of the detector was determined",
                "with a Ra-226 and a Sc-46 source.",
                "The energies in the gamma spectrum were determined",
                "with Cs-137,Co-57,Co-60,ra-226,Sc-46,Na-22 and Th-C''."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "PART-DET": [
